Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.07,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already been three days\Nsince that incident in the forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.28,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't seen any of them since...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or even heard from them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.21,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Inoue still hasn't been found, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.25,0:03:18.26,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our everyday lives have come to an end.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.26,0:03:23.13,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Kanbe-san, Konohana-san,\Nand Ohtori-san are out sick again today.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.13,0:03:26.55,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,There seems to be a cold going around,\Nso please be careful, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.76,0:03:30.01,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Lucia and Shizuru are members\Nof a secret organization called Guardian,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.01,0:03:34.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}while Prez and Chihaya are members\Nof their enemy organization, Gaia.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.05,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}That's why they disappeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.05,0:03:37.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}That much makes sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.95,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why Kotori? She had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.28,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,The Harvest Festa is coming soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.72,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Stay focused,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.72,0:03:46.73,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,and act responsibly as students\Nof Kazamatsuri Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.16,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,That will be all.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.31,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Hey, is Kanbe absent again today?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.76,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, looks like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.33,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,It's not just her,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.31,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,but Konohana and Ohtori, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.22,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Everyone who hangs out with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.52,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.44,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,There's a cold going around, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.35,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,If you really are in trouble...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.05,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.15,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.18,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's one other thing that bothers me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.86,0:04:29.41,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there more to my power than\Njust rewriting my physical abilities
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.62,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}and enhancing myself?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.38,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.58,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I think they're around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.52,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Found them!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Let's see just how sharp they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.07,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I-It sliced right through them!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I totally gotta try this out on all sorts of stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Did I leave the window open?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.91,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Tennouji...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.14,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kotarou...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.14,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.27,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.27,0:05:43.59,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,This is... an emergency.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.21,0:05:46.97,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.12,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.32,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,She wasn't a ghost?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.12,0:05:57.33,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,I have something to announce\Nregarding Inoue-san from Class 2-A,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.63,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,who went missing a few days ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were told that as of a few days ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inoue had been admitted to\Na hospital the next town over.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.74,0:06:12.62,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were only told about this now\Nbecause Inoue's memory was foggy,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.35,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it'd taken some time to identify her.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.85,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}While her memory hadn't cleared up yet,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.29,0:06:23.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}the fact that she hadn't sustained\Nany physical injuries was a silver lining.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.97,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, it was such a huge shock to her parents
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.97,0:06:30.32,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}that Inoue's whole family\Nended up leaving Kazamatsuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.75,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,If she saw this...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.84,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Lucia would get mad at you,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.34,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.80,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sh-Shizuru?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.26,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wh-Where have you been this whole time?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.49,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.35,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.70,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.98,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.19,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,So please, lead a happy life.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.36,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wait, Shizuru!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.42,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,The occult club was a lot of fun. I loved it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Shizuru!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.64,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Did someone break in?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.10,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It was her, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.73,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,She's not here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.95,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I sense something strange in... here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.95,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.22,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.22,0:08:18.73,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.72,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It was a feint!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.86,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,My name is Kagari-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.86,0:08:26.96,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.23,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,To be blunt, that's all I remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.09,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,So you're an amnesiac ghost?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.42,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I'm not a ghost. I'm Kagari-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.56,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.56,0:08:40.06,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I believe I was on some sort of important mission...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.06,0:08:43.75,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,That is why I need to find myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.01,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I need to find myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.01,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You want my help?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.57,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What a strange dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.95,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah, I knew it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.63,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm going to school.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.99,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Crap. What am I gonna do about her?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.99,0:09:22.55,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,You should help me out instead\Nof bothering with school right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.86,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Don't be unreasonable.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Search for yourself by yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.54,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I don't know how.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.54,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Go on a trip or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.29,0:09:30.80,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.80,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could I get you to leave\Nthe room for a minute?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.30,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Are you trying to hide something from me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.90,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Won't you {\i1}please{\i0} leave for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.23,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,What in the world have you been\Ndoing for the last five minutes?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Simply being a modest gentleman.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.64,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Do not concern yourself over it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.86,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,More importantly, behold! The Internet!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.40,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Humans manage to shop and find\Ntheir way through life on the Internet.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.75,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I guess even at times like these, you get hungry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.01,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Why can't I go into the classroom?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.59,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,You're not in this class, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.89,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Hurry back to your own homeroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.82,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell is she doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.60,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait. Everyone else can see her this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.60,0:10:32.39,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I found on the Internet that Tennouji Kotarou\Nwas attending someplace interesting,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.43,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,so I got jeal—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.30,Default - Alt,GirlA,0,0,0,,Tennouji?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.61,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I found that unforgivable and transferred in.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.61,Default - Alt,GirlB,0,0,0,,She knows him?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.65,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.65,0:10:37.86,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Say what you will,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.87,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,common sense dictates that suspicious\Npeople should be sent to the staff room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.58,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Don't think badly of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.79,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Yoshino-kun got destroyed!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.05,Default,Boy2,0,0,0,,That transfer student's strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.05,Default,Boy3,0,0,0,,It's the birth of a new gang leader!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.64,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It's your fault for being mean\Nand leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.41,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,No matter how much you\Nsuper-duper totally love me,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.41,0:11:10.13,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,you should be more straightforward about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.52,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hold on. What did you just say?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.85,0:11:16.22,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I know that human males tend to be mean
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.78,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,to the females that they like.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.83,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I learned {\i1}all{\i0} about humans on the Internet.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.90,0:11:24.56,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Have I left you utterly speechless?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.04,0:11:29.54,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Next, I will learn about myself\Nin this institution you call a school.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.72,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Schools will only teach you academics.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.67,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,How petty...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.00,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'll show you around the building,\Nso try to make do with that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.43,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kay-o!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.13,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Way to go, Tennouji Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.58,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,"K-Kay-o"?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.58,0:11:46.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Just Kotarou is fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.18,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Saying the whole thing is annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.60,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Okay, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.85,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,By the way, what's with that uniform?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.58,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,These clothes are part of my body,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.73,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,so I can transform them freely.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.29,0:12:02.24,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I'm fabulous down to my very core,\Nso praise me, human.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.74,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I knew you definitely weren't human.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.62,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,First, this is the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.54,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,As you can see, this is where\Npeople eat their meals.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.67,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.24,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It's a place where you sate\Nyour appetites by devouring
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.24,0:12:17.50,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,other lifeforms that inhabit the same planet.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.37,0:12:20.76,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Uh, well, you're not wrong...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.62,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,In that case, I desire shi-su!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,There ain't any.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.80,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why'd you suddenly start having worldly desires?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.08,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.32,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a self-service coffee machine.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.02,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Feecof?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.74,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Th-This is... myyum!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.90,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}They have a reputation for using\Nsuch abysmally cheap beans
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.85,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}that you wouldn't want to drink it, even for free...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.85,0:12:51.41,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I'm positive this must have come from\Nthe hands of a renowned feecof artisan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.94,0:12:54.68,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Who created this feecof?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.07,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I am asking for the hostess!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.55,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I would like to give my compliments directly\Nto the human who made this—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.21,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sorry for the disturbance!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.71,0:13:07.92,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I rushed out of there without thinking\Nand ended up skipping afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.49,0:13:12.62,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Your love will come across as oppressive\Nif you're too mean, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.62,0:13:17.07,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,As a sign of your love, you should offer me\Nthree months' salary worth of feecof.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.31,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,How much do you wanna drink?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.65,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been a while since I've done something like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.26,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I-Inoue!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.09,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What happened in that forest in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.29,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.03,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.67,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.37,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Who were you again?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.03,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.02,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.26,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.00,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,You know me?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.00,0:13:52.75,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.75,0:13:54.90,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You appointed me as your rival.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.89,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,What were we rivals in?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Chasing after the mysteries of Kazamatsuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.39,0:14:01.89,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You were in the newspaper club,\Nand I was in the occult club.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.89,0:14:02.94,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.15,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,I was in the newspaper club?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.04,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Mysteries, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.89,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.16,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,A memory card?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.84,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,I haven't checked what's on it,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.84,0:14:19.51,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,but apparently I was holding onto it tightly,\Nrefusing to let go,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.51,0:14:22.17,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,even when I was unconscious.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.78,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Something tells me I need to give this to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.78,0:14:26.44,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.44,0:14:28.18,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,But I'm sure what's on this is—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.37,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.85,0:14:34.20,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure this is what I came here to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.72,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Yeah, bye bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,About our competition...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.28,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You win!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.00,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.85,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.57,0:15:03.33,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,A piece of that human's heart has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.04,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.04,0:15:07.42,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,And yet, she accomplished\Nher objective all the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.95,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,She entrusted it to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.92,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I didn't know you could do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.73,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,The Kagari-chan exploration party has returned!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.40,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Don't loiter around my house so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.36,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It is quite spacious.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.47,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,For you to own this all by yourself,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.75,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,you must have done something\Nquite underhanded.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.15,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Don't make me sound so shady.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,My parents are the ones who built it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.58,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,By "parents," you mean your genetic contributors?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.03,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I have not seen any sign of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,They're busy with work.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,They're researchers,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and they mostly stay over at work.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.57,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It's a corporation associated
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,with the environmental protection agency\Nknown as the Martel Group.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.97,Default,Suza,0,0,0,,It appears you have returned, Senri.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.71,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.85,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,My apologies for having been\Nout of touch for so long, Suzaki-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.16,Default,Suza,0,0,0,,There was never any need for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.16,0:16:03.40,Default,Suza,0,0,0,,the next saint, to attend school.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.61,Default,Suza,0,0,0,,In future, please know your\Nrole and act accordingly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.01,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Accursed girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.87,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Are you finished...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.37,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,with greetings?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.18,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.18,0:16:26.17,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Now, please get started.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.96,Default,Suza,0,0,0,,So then, regarding the Key's movements.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.32,0:16:32.71,Default,Suza,0,0,0,,We haven't been able to pin down its location
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.97,Default,Suza,0,0,0,,since we detected its presence\Nin the city the other day—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.47,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.85,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I'm back, Shimako.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.70,0:16:52.99,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Akane-san, it's absolutely\Nfilled with cobwebs here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.49,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I was planning to clean them up later!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.49,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,An elementary schooler's excuse,\Nif I ever heard one.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.08,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Is the meeting over?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.08,0:17:02.94,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.29,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Call it a meeting if you like,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.42,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,but I was just put on wheelchair\Nduty the whole time.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.38,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,It's been like that all the time lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.38,0:17:13.55,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,When a saint is knocking on death's door,\Nthey keep their successor close at hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.01,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,And she's abiding by that old custom.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.14,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.35,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Kashima Sakura's days are numbered?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.75,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nwhere is the item I asked you for?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.10,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.93,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.65,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.58,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I was in such a hurry that\NI couldn't bring it with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.69,0:17:36.31,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,At last, I have returned...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.24,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,to the motherly embrace of cyberspace!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.24,0:17:43.62,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Such unbecoming, vulgar words\Nfrom the next Martel... no, Gaia saint.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.62,0:17:46.24,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Still, I'm sure it never occurred\Nto Tennouji and the others
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.91,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,that the club room and the\NMartel Japanese headquarters
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.58,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,were connected via a hidden passage.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.92,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Club activities were a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.79,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,They may be our enemies,\Nbut I'm glad we became friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.22,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Um, are Kotarou and Kotori all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.22,0:18:10.67,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I mean, they found out our secret and everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.67,0:18:13.47,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,In regards to that female \Nstudent from the other day,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.47,0:18:16.77,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Lady Akane found out what happened to her
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.45,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,and sheltered her without any further incident.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.22,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,There is a danger that as a witness,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.70,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,a mark has been placed upon\NTennouji by both sides.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.46,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Um, what about Kotori?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.68,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Kanbe is...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.94,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.09,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I don't have any conclusive proof yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.74,0:18:37.84,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,It appears we will need to take\Nsome precautionary measures.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.63,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Lucia.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.99,0:19:14.46,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It sacrificed its mobility\Nwithout so much as a struggle.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.21,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Did it underestimate us?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.74,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Now, Shizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.74,0:19:26.93,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Exact your revenge.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.23,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.79,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Looks like it's all over, huh, Shizuru-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.79,0:19:42.62,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Gramps.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.88,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's over, but this isn't the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.88,0:19:46.88,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.98,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Esaka-san, what about the summoner?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.67,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,I struck him with my sword, but he got away.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.17,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,That was fine work, you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.47,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,You've grown.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.49,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Shizuru-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.16,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.55,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,You're not hurt or anything, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.11,0:20:02.97,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.89,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,W-We have finished cleaning up\Nthe daemons in this area, Instructor!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.06,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,I mean, Esaka-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.65,0:20:12.68,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,It has been some time since I retired,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.68,0:20:15.18,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,but our enemy has become quite sloppy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.18,0:20:18.46,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Kazamatsuri is holy ground\Nfor the followers of Gaia,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.46,0:20:21.42,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,so various summoners gather here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.20,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Do you suppose this is due to the Key?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.20,0:20:27.70,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,There seems to be little other reason\Nfor such an abundance of daemons
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.89,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,to be deployed to the city and forest\Nbefore the Harvest Festa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.89,0:20:30.97,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Esaka-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.97,0:20:34.45,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,I am most grateful that all of you veterans\Nhave returned to the front lines.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.46,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,A storm is coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.85,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Steel yourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.85,0:20:38.96,Default,all,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.58,0:20:40.46,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.72,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I've got a job for you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.36,0:20:46.97,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,If I recall, you are Gil-san and Pani-san, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.12,0:20:49.93,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.06,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,The crude sin you committed\Nagainst Chihaya-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.28,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,It appears you will finally be able to make up for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.07,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}After getting stranded in the forest,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.36,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inoue left behind notes
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.36,0:21:09.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}detailing her close encounters with the\Nmany daemons and mysterious robed men.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.08,0:21:14.63,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her declaration that organizations\Nlikely lurked in the underbelly of Kazamatsuri,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}accusations of the danger they posed,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}and admitting that the occult was real,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.53,0:21:22.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}all must have amounted to\Na concession speech to her, in a way.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.38,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must have been so upset.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.60,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Please switch with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.93,0:21:32.11,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,The next part of the web comic\NI am interested in came out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.11,0:21:33.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey, don't mess with it from the side.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.79,0:21:34.73,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.23,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.23,0:21:41.45,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Something about this place bothers me.
